race.comment: FOREVER FORTUNE (1) didn't measure up in town two back before not being too far away at Lismore last time out. Will be rock-hard fit for this and can make his presence felt. CAIRO QUEEN (7) gets 3kg off from the inside marble and will be cherry-ripe for this fourth-up. Looms as the main danger. THE HOPSTAR (10) will be better for race experience after debuting here a week and a half ago. Can feature with natural improvement. ARTISTIC TOUCH (6) will be rock-hard fit for this after four runs back and may earn some minor money with any luck in running. OHH ERROL (4) next in line from the Bruce stable.
